commit.message:
unwind-dw2.c (execute_stack_op): Add missing cases for DW_OP_shl, DW_OP_shr, DW_OP_shra, DW_OP_xor.

	* unwind-dw2.c (execute_stack_op): Add missing cases for
	DW_OP_shl, DW_OP_shr, DW_OP_shra, DW_OP_xor.
